toast_messages: Enabling or Disabling a constellation will cause an automatic restart of Kronos.
Select which constellations to use. Either GLONASS or BeiDou can be selected, not both.
Changing Antenna Delay will cause an automatic restart of Kronos.
Disabling Antenna Simulation will cause an automatic restart of Kronos.
Low Quality and Bad Time values are in milliseconds. Low Quality valid values are from 0.001 (1 microsecond) to 4000 (4 seconds).
